These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, indie, rock, soul
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, lemonade, juice, 7up
House: ranch-style, cottage, tower, victorian
1. the fan of indie is on the right of the victorian house##1
2. the victorian house is between the person drinking lemonade and the fan of folk##2
3. the cottage house is on the far left##1
4. the cottage house is on the left of the fan of rock##1
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the tower house##1
6. the person drinking juice is on the right of the fan of indie##1
7. the victorian house is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | folk    | rock      | indie      | soul    |
| Beverage   | 7up | hot-chocolate | lemonade | juice |
| House     | cottage    | victorian       | tower     | ranch-style     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-2::.
There 4 different types of food: avocado, corn, cucumber, peach
House: futuristic, ranch-style, palace, cape-cod
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: aconite, orchid, rose, lily
1. the ranch-style house is on the far left##1
2. the person eating avocado is on the left of the person eating peach##1
3. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person eating corn##1
4. the person who growslily is on the far left##1
5. the person who growslily is on the left or right of the palace house##3
6. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the person eating corn##1
7. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the futuristic house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |      4      |
| Food          | avocado     | peach     | corn       | cucumber    |
| House         | ranch-style | palace   | futuristic | cape-cod |
| Flower   | lily    | rose | orchid    | aconite        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, fanta, soy-milk
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: orchid, sunflower, iris, begonia
House: cape-cod, cottage, art-deco, farmhouse
1. the person who growssunflower is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the person who growsiris##3
3. the art-deco house is on the left or right of the person who growsorchid##3
4. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
5. the person who growsiris is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
7. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left##1
8. the art-deco house is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3     |    4     |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | coffee  | fanta    | soy-milk |
| Flower   | iris   | begonia  | orchid  | sunflower    |
| House         | cottage    | farmhouse | cape-cod | art-deco  |

