.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-4::.
City: rome, boston, edinburgh, london
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, disco, rock, indie
4 different pets are kept: dog, goat, lizard, turtle
1. the owner of the goat is between the fan of disco and the person traveling to rome##2
2. the fan of d&b is on the left or right of the fan of disco##3
3. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
4. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the far left##1
5. the owner of the dog is the person traveling to london##1
6. the fan of disco is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
7. the person traveling to london is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
8. the fan of indie is on the left or right of the person traveling to boston##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |    3     |     4     |
| City          | edinburgh   | rome     | boston | london |
| Music-Genre   | rock | indie | d&b   | disco     |
| Pet           | turtle | lizard      | goat     | dog       |

