.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-5::.
House: art-deco, tower, palace, farmhouse
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, dressmaker, lawyer, librarian
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, lemonade, mirinda, sprite
1. the art-deco house is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the tower house##3
3. the lawyer is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
4. the architect is between the palace house and the tower house##2
5. the lawyer is on the right of the librarian##1
6. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
7. the palace house is on the left or right of the farmhouse house##3
8. the palace house is the person drinking mirinda##1
9. the tower house is on the left or right of the farmhouse house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| House          | palace      | farmhouse | tower      | art-deco |
| Job           | dressmaker | architect | librarian | lawyer   |
| Beverage   | mirinda    | sprite   | lemonade     | hot-chocolate   |

