.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, doctor, entrepreneur, videographer
City: london, marseilles, paris, boston
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, may, march, february
1. the person who's birthday is in may is the coach##1
2. the person who's birthday is in march is the person traveling to boston##1
3. the coach is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
4. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in march##3
5. the person traveling to paris is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in may##3
6. the entrepreneur is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
7. the doctor is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
8. the doctor is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |      3       |      4       |
| Job           | coach    | doctor   | entrepreneur | videographer |
| City   | london     | paris   | boston         | marseilles        |
| Birthday         | may | july | march         | february       |

