.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-7::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, pall-mall, baccarat, montecristo
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, dancer, doctor, videographer
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, sprite, fanta, hot-chocolate
 1. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
 2. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the baccarat-smoker##3
 3. the montecristo-smoker is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
 4. the doctor is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
 5. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the pall-mall-smoker##1
 6. the baccarat-smoker is the baccarat-smoker##1
 7. the doctor is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1
 8. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the videographer##3
 9. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the pall-mall-smoker##1
10. the dancer is on the left or right of the doctor##3
11. the dancer is the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| Cigar         | baccarat    | dunhill  | pall-mall | montecristo   |
| Job           | videographer | dancer   | doctor    | bartender |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate      | fanta | sprite | soy-milk  |

