.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-8::.
House: townhouse, gothic-revival, art-deco, cape-cod
4 different games are played: canasta, backgammon, go, mah-jongg
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, mystery, spy, western
1. the person playing backgammon is on the left or right of the gothic-revival house##3
2. the person watching action movies is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
3. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the person playing go##3
4. the person watching spy movies is on the far right##1
5. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the art-deco house##1
6. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
7. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left or right of the cape-cod house##3
8. the person playing go is on the left or right of the person playing mah-jongg##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |      4      |
| House          | art-deco | gothic-revival    | cape-cod | townhouse    |
| Game         | go     | mah-jongg | backgammon  | canasta |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery    | western      | action   | spy         |

