.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-9::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, ritmeester, baccarat, bluemaster
The people have 4 different jobs:  doctor, dressmaker, nurse, security-guard
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: volleyball, soccer, snowboarding, rugby
1. the dressmaker is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the doctor##1
3. the vegafina-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
4. the nurse is on the right of the security-guard##1
5. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far right##1
6. the baccarat-smoker is on the left of the bluemaster-smoker##1
7. the security-guard is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
8. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |     3     |     4      |
| Cigar      | ritmeester    | baccarat            | bluemaster     | vegafina      |
| Job           | doctor    | security-guard | nurse     | dressmaker |
| Sport   | volleyball | snowboarding    | soccer | rugby    |

