.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-10::.
There 4 different types of food: cauliflower, garlic, nectarine, raspberry
House: futuristic, cottage, palace, farmhouse
4 different games are played: scrabble, snooker, whist, bridge
1. the palace house is on the far left or far right##3
2. the palace house is on the left of the person eating nectarine##1
3. the person eating garlic is on the left or right of the person playing snooker##3
4. the person eating raspberry is on the far right##1
5. the farmhouse house is the person eating raspberry##1
6. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person eating cauliflower##1
7. the cottage house is on the left of the person playing whist##1
8. the person eating garlic is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Food          | garlic   | nectarine | cauliflower | raspberry |
| House   | palace   | cottage     | futuristic      | farmhouse  |
| Game   | scrabble | snooker   | whist    | bridge   |

