.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-11::.
There are 4 different nationalities: spanish, australian, russian, dutch
4 different games are played: domino, bridge, billiard, snooker
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, lacrosse, rowing, skateboarding
1. the australian is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
2. the person playing domino is on the left or right of the dutch##3
3. the person playing domino is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
4. the russian is on the right of the spanish##1
5. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
6. the person playing domino is on the left or right of the person playing bridge##3
7. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
8. the person who's sport is biathlon is the person playing snooker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |       2       |     3      |   4    |
| Nationality           | dutch | australian        | spanish   | russian  |
| Game   | bridge             | domino     | snooker | billiard  |
| Sport         | lacrosse           | skateboarding | biathlon   | rowing |

