The people have 4 different jobs:  nurse, project-manager, teacher, writer
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, colombian, indonesian, argentine
1. the writer is on the right of the indonesian##1
2. the colombian is on the far left##1
3. the argentine is on the right of the project-manager##1
4. the person who growsdahlia is on the left or right of the teacher##3
5. the person who growsdahlia is on the left or right of the teacher##3
6. the argentine is between the colombian and the person who growszinnia##2
7. the person who growsdahlia is the project-manager##1
8. the person who growspoppy is on the left or right of the person who growsdahlia##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |        1        |     2      |     3      |   4    |
| Flower    | dahlia   | poppy   | zinnia    | rose |
| Job         | project-manager | teacher    | nurse      | writer |
| Nationality   | colombian      | argentine | indonesian | chinese   |

