.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-13::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, cricket, skiing, biathlon
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, traveling, woodworking, writing
House: palace, tower, craftsman, townhouse
1. the person who's sport is tennis is the palace house##1
2. the person who's hobby is board-games is between the person who's sport is cricket and the person who's hobby is writing##2
3. the person who's hobby is traveling is the townhouse house##1
4. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##3
5. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
6. the person who's sport is cricket is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
7. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far left##1
8. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
9. the craftsman house is the person who's hobby is writing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Sport    | cricket      | tennis | biathlon       | skiing  |
| Hobby       | woodworking | board-games | writing    | traveling |
| House   | tower     | palace         | craftsman | townhouse     |

