.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-14::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: blood-red, red, yellow, turquise
House: wooden, farmhouse, colonial, art-deco
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, animation, romance, time-travel
1. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
2. the person who likes yellow is the wooden house##1
3. the art-deco house is on the far left or far right##3
4. the art-deco house is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
5. the farmhouse house is on the left or right of the person who likes yellow##3
6. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
7. the person who likes red is the person watching adventure movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |      2      |     3     |     4     |
