.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-17::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, july, february, october
The people have 4 different jobs:  photographer, videographer, engineer, architect
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, ship, snowmobile, tram
1. the videographer is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
2. the person who's birthday is in july is the architect##1
3. the videographer is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
4. the person driving the ship is between the person driving the scooter and the person driving the snowmobile##2
5. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far left or far right##3
6. the photographer is on the far left##1
7. the architect is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in october##3
8. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |      2      |      3      |      4      |
| Birthday    | february   | october    | july      | april |
| Job       | photographer  | videographer | architect | engineer     |
| Transport   | scooter | ship        | snowmobile  | tram        |

