6. the person eating mango is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
7. the cain-smoker is the person playing canasta##1
8. the person eating asparagus is between the cain-smoker and the siglo-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |     4     |
