5. the person drinking milk is between the person traveling to nizza and the person traveling to colone##2
6. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the security-guard##3
7. the person drinking lemonade is on the far right##1
8. the person traveling to colone is on the left or right of the journalist##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |    3     |       4        |
| City    | colone | paris  | nizza  | san-francisco           |
| Job     | bartender | journalist | dancer   | security-guard |
| Beverage   | sprite   | milk       | almond-milk | lemonade  |

 